<section class="sb-section sb-section--deep sb-prob-sol" id="SbProblemSolution">
  <details class="sb-mobile-collapse">
    <summary class="sb-mobile-collapse__toggle">
      The Problem &amp; Solution <span class="sb-mobile-collapse__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    </summary>
    <div class="sb-container sb-prob-sol__grid">

      {%- comment -%} LEFT — Problem {%- endcomment -%}
      <div class="sb-prob-sol__col">
        <span class="sb-eyebrow">The Problem</span>
        <h2 class="sb-prob-sol__headline">Your morning drink is working against you.</h2>
        <p class="sb-prob-sol__body">Most of us start the day the same way. A cup of coffee. Maybe two. A jolt of cortisol, a spike in blood sugar, then — three hours later — the crash. Energy drinks promise more and deliver less. Typical wellness teas are under-dosed or taste like lawn clippings. Most of what's marketed as healthy is loaded with artificial sweeteners, gum fillers, seed oils, and vague proprietary blends that tell you nothing.</p>

        <blockquote class="sb-pull-quote">
          <p>"Your body wants to thrive. It is literally designed for it — built with an extraordinary capacity to self-regulate, detoxify, and regenerate. The problem is most of us are giving it the wrong inputs every single morning."</p>
          <footer class="sb-pull-quote__attribution">— The Spellbinder Formulator</footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>

      {%- comment -%} RIGHT — Solution {%- endcomment -%}
      <div class="sb-prob-sol__col">
        <span class="sb-eyebrow">The Solution</span>
        <p class="sb-prob-sol__display">The world's first Biological Intelligence elixir system.</p>
        <p class="sb-prob-sol__body">Created by a microbiologist at the crossroads of ancient Eastern herbalism and modern Western biochemistry. Every ingredient is chosen with purpose. Every formula is built on one governing idea:</p>

        <div class="sb-highlight-box">
          <p>When you give the body the right synergistic inputs — rooted in tradition, validated by science — it knows exactly what to do with them. That is Biological Intelligence.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </details>
</section>

